<br />
<br />    Since May, I've been very busy on a revenue generating project, plus the work-load at my day job has increased significantly.  So I put my nesdev stuff on hold.  I doubt that I'll be picking it up anytime soon. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" title="Sad" />
<br />
<br />    I'm also a bit bummed out that Atari has begun suing everyone and anyone who has created a fan work (web sites, game ports, etc...) so I'm not sure what I'll do with my Yars' Revenge clone.  The obvious answer is to change the graphics, text and sound.  But that doesn't seem very satisfying.
<br />
<br />    I'm posting to say hello.  I didn't want anyone to think that I was trying to be rude or that I had disappeared.

		

